{"id":"a86de4f1-c8f9-44b3-9833-dfc792f83ffc","title":"1552/02/20: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"fbb2aeba-e981-4be8-91a1-41dceab8282e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, February 20th, 1552.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"4b1d1a9b-1957-479e-8eed-27cda79b9646","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"97ea2ca3-c18b-4973-b4bc-216bf07d815f","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"cab905e1-16dd-44da-8545-4ad8be4020b1","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a7e904e0-cec3-42cd-b32f-94de00b5df8a","type":"style/superscript","start":22,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b627fc7f-ef11-4577-971f-36413a3bbadf","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"188a7f3b-f52a-437f-838b-8164f3982add","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"877a2101-11c8-4272-9299-5db9243b03c4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b2605029-264d-4991-911e-25221a96df80","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6faf75b2-04e1-4620-aad3-70596934bab8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"56f109b0-1620-48c0-87fe-56c2fa2f6cc9","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bece19d8-62d5-452f-abce-7d3e8a97bafe","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have had a conversation here with the girl\u0027s uncle, who said he was very much surprised that we should throw her over, and that some avaricious person desirous of obtaining the dowry for\u00A0himself or of inheriting her property must have interfered. I deem it advisable to tell thee what\u00A0has been said. A letter of thine has just been brought in as I sit writing, in which thou tellest me of a daughter of Carlo di Giovanni Strozzi. I knew Giovanni Strozzi when I was a lad, and he was a worthy fellow\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I\u00A0cannot say more about him. I also knew Carlo, so that I think the match might be a good one.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c6e3ce36-c087-416c-8e1f-6f16e14fd543","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"90d23df0-f886-41be-922f-ee15d7adc72f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0839e5b0-0b88-429b-894e-b8812fb700c6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2d204c29-be84-4e9d-ab99-c6b1cbf8c14e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":41,"value":"6d6e9df9-6e15-4e85-867d-4e4d3bb04ccf","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b1ec7077-29b5-4af3-883c-90c255752e03","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":52,"end":55,"value":"f11ba55e-ccdb-4fa1-8641-3e9067510efb","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ad298302-ebf4-4614-8d70-0abc4de62f6f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":59,"end":63,"value":"c685d0c7-aed2-46d8-b289-4e0452a6fe77","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3a8e784e-6b24-4c36-8d67-9409a838bb77","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":66,"end":68,"value":"c685d0c7-aed2-46d8-b289-4e0452a6fe77","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c6b2ded8-b850-47f6-9732-25d6af7fee17","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":75,"end":76,"value":"c685d0c7-aed2-46d8-b289-4e0452a6fe77","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"70c58082-55d0-453b-b96e-73cb04c7b1ba","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":107,"end":108,"value":"76b25272-e3d0-4804-b521-f9641b6eec2d","zero