off-editor-block","text":"As to the property mentioned by thee, I do not want one near Florence; it would be more suitable if\u00A0it were in Chianti. Therefore, if thou shouldst find a good investment I am ready to buy it, and I am not particular as to a couple of hundred crowns.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"89a194d1-801b-4b7f-86c7-6df281621e4c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":10,"end":17,"value":"8ab5e2f1-45ba-4ac2-9084-1e9332bfa006","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bf93dd40-a5e6-4e97-81ff-a24d7d6d257e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":32,"end":35,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"50af0f17-0a9e-4381-85e5-e8d87df2ebc3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":38,"end":38,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"afb33a9e-3373-46e7-825f-fd585ab4df1f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":61,"end":68,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a1d22df8-38a7-4d4c-92aa-06a3cb77f217","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":100,"end":101,"value":"8ab5e2f1-45ba-4ac2-9084-1e9332bfa006","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2d072733-3d8b-40ab-8262-c27a098216b3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":111,"end":117,"value":"9923bd78-7f30-4805-8723-d9f8422ae2a2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0530769a-4cf7-4afb-a641-21bd9a0f1f60","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":134,"end":137,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"23484cf8-2bce-4db0-9837-8c75491a646b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":160,"end":169,"value":"7930c99c-441e-4c70-b6a9-d4dcf17280d8","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"a3860330-fbfd-4e4b-b71e-8270f5505ac1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":171,"end":171,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f56500c8-57cc-461a-9961-cf256dce12a7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":189,"end":190,"value":"7930c99c-441e-4c70-b6a9-d4dcf17280d8","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"30d995c1-4032-4324-b5db-c71750f231a4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":197,"end":197,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c5858814-cab8-4f7b-afe4-edf47c35d437","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7f2aaf53-f64a-4b56-a714-b09323fecfa7","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As to thy choice of a wife, I have no opportunity\u00A0of hearing about anything here, for I have no intercourse with the Florentines and still less with other\u00A0people.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"02605672-edd3-47e6-8a29-d03fc8106c92","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":6,"end":8,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"12ddb726-69b3-4968-afae-adfc4ebecbb5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":22,"end":25,"value":"85764433-0e1c-44ab-9822-e6c389b39ef7","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"efe2b1bc-cf3e-4d46-8c27-d334482c2ef4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":28,"end":28,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4949190c-312c-4f55-ab47-4f5e6215d6b7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":76,"end":79,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"857e974a-03bc-458f-9e61-15c9a65d8b57","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":86,"end":86,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"e3430eaf-2b4d-439c-a8cd-3f13d7958a9e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2c583f1e-8464-426a-bdd7-e4ddd104371f","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"I am old, as I said in my last letter, and in order to avoid raising anybody\u0027s hopes needlessly, if anybody should have cherished such hopes, I am thinking of making a will in which all I have in Florence will be left to my brother Gismondo and to thee, my nephew, with the stipulation that neither of ye shall be free to touch any of it without the consent of the\u00A0other. If thou shouldst die without legitimate heirs everything is to go to San Martino; that is to say, the income is to be given to poor people for the love of\u00A0God, that is to say to impoverished citizens, or to be laid out in any better may ye may be able to suggest.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"8db799cf-5e98-45b8-9725-f4e92278199c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":0,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"98d912ec-f86a-4f32-b1b0-f826252b6956","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":13,"end":13,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"44bd786e-bf16-42d8-8224-ccdffeaa1381","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":23,"end":24,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7ce9fd68-ea96-4277-90f0-0ae57cc9c7c6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":69,"end":75,"value":"f3508101-204b-4510-be96-2c25b30889d4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b018b529-7357-419d-9b48-a232e1f4f154","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":100,"end":106,"value":"f3508101-204b-4510-be96-2c25b30889d4","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9ff42c7f-2ed6-4353-a971-aa5c2500fce4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":142,"end":142,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2974cd0a-30f8-4c71-b951-aff21ffcac57","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":186,"end":186,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1c672aa5-a7fa-42ba-b8c0-7acdf75958ac","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":188,"end":191,"value":"ad5dc25e-523b-4829-9918-1adc4a0410ab","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7453050e-6d17-4015-9e86-936acc0acd59","type":"codex/entity-reference","sta